--[[
üéØ HOW TO USE NVIM-SURROUND:

1. ADD SURROUND:
   ‚Ä¢ Position cursor on word: hello
   ‚Ä¢ Type: ysiw"
   ‚Ä¢ Result: "hello"

   ‚Ä¢ Position cursor anywhere on line: local x = 42
   ‚Ä¢ Type: yss)
   ‚Ä¢ Result: (local x = 42)

2. DELETE SURROUND:
   ‚Ä¢ Position cursor inside: "hello"
   ‚Ä¢ Type: ds"
   ‚Ä¢ Result: hello

3. CHANGE SURROUND:
   ‚Ä¢ Position cursor inside: "hello"
   ‚Ä¢ Type: cs"'
   ‚Ä¢ Result: 'hello'

   ‚Ä¢ Position cursor inside: [hello]
   ‚Ä¢ Type: cs])
   ‚Ä¢ Result: (hello)

4. VISUAL MODE:
   ‚Ä¢ Select text: hello world
   ‚Ä¢ Type: S"
   ‚Ä¢ Result: "hello world"

5. ADVANCED EXAMPLES:
   ‚Ä¢ ysiw}     ‚Üí {word}
   ‚Ä¢ ysiwt     ‚Üí <tag>word</tag> (prompts for tag)
   ‚Ä¢ yss<p>    ‚Üí <p>entire line</p>
   ‚Ä¢ cs"<em>   ‚Üí "text" becomes <em>text</em>

6. REMEMBER:
   ‚Ä¢ Open brackets: ( [ { add spaces ‚Üí ( text )
   ‚Ä¢ Close brackets: ) ] } no spaces ‚Üí (text)
   ‚Ä¢ Most punctuation works: " ' ` ~ + = - *

7. CUSTOM ONES (from config):
